{"tid":697150,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"將軍澳海水化淡廠工程進度！","createTime":"2018-06-10T17:13:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-23T14:14:19.000Z","uid":70063,"like":156,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"9a425ae144cd8a654a00b05aca95321ff2f24d2e","tid":697150,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T17:13:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.vjmedia.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/29/173095/24232640_1515920671837134_3617249788188932537_n.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.vjmedia.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F11%2F29%2F173095%2F24232640_1515920671837134_3617249788188932537_n.png&h=8a868e95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>工程範圍</strong><br />\n<br />\n將軍澳海水化淡廠第一階段工程項目包括下列主要部分：<br />\n<br />\n1. 興建第一階段的擬議海水化淡廠，每日食水產量可達13萬5千立方米，並會預留空間以便日後可擴展至最終產水量為每日27萬立方米，以及相關設施；<br />\n<br />\n2. 在將軍澳第 137 區平整已預留的8 公頃土地，以興建最終食水產量達每日27萬立方米的海水化淡廠及相關設施；<br />\n<br />\n3. 為擬議海水化淡廠興建進水管道和排放管道，其容量足以應付海水化淡廠最終達每日27萬立方米的食水產量；<br />\n<br />\n4. 進行相關的工程包括環境影響緩解措施、斜坡鞏固和環境美化工程；以及<br />\n<br />\n5. 進行相關的敷設水管工程，以輸送擬議海水化淡廠生產的食水至現有將軍澳食水主配水庫。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>目前進度</strong><br />\n<br />\n正在招標階段 (工程範圍中第一至第四項目)<br />\n<br />\n正在施工階段 (工程範圍中第五項目)<br />\n<br />\n<strong>水務署項目辦公室</strong><br />\n<br />\n顧問工程管理部 (負責工程範圍中第一至第四項目)<br />\n<br />\n建設部 (負責工程範圍中第五項目)<br />\n<br />\n<strong>項目顧問</strong><br />\n<br />\n博威工程顧問有限公司 (負責工程範圍中第一至第四項目)<br />\n<br />\n<strong>合約</strong><br />\n<br />\n13/WSD/16 將軍澳水管敷設工程 (工程範圍中第五項目)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.wsd.gov.hk/tc/core-businesses/major-infrastructure-projects/tko-desalination-plant/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsd.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fcore-businesses%2Fmajor-infrastructure-projects%2Ftko-desalination-plant%2Findex.html&d=7dik%2B57InS7eQz7adFhe%2FW6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=697973e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.wsd.gov.hk/tc/core-businesses/major-infrastructure-projects/tko-desalination-plant/index.html</a>"},{"pid":"957150d0de308d50189ce1eb53b645198a80eb74","tid":697150,"uid":141151,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T17:16:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4486ea443f9e5346baf8b7e6aeab1b44881e76e5","tid":697150,"uid":70063,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"957150d0de308d50189ce1eb53b645198a80eb74","tid":697150,"uid":141151,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T17:16:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T17:33:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e40437d31918a355293672f5ceeca959e9926b2f","tid":697150,"uid":24345,"like":133,"dislike":3,"score":130,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T17:50:15.000Z","msg":"保皇狗都投贊成，民主黨嗰幾條撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0dd01a7003810eb2265266667b91e00662d8129","tid":697150,"uid":47359,"like":36,"dislike":5,"score":31,"quote":{"pid":"e40437d31918a355293672f5ceeca959e9926b2f","tid":697150,"uid":24345,"like":133,"dislike":3,"score":130,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T17:50:15.000Z","msg":"保皇狗都投贊成，民主黨嗰幾條撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T17:54:50.000Z","msg":"@五毛狙擊手<br />\n@真俊華<br />\n@慕清流<br />\n<br />\n樓主踢爆泛民啲衰嘢噉佢係咪鬼?"},{"pid":"0211caad06ad8f6312994a5f5d66f21fdbff39dc","tid":697150,"uid":47359,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"f0dd01a7003810eb2265266667b91e00662d8129","tid":697150,"uid":47359,"like":36,"dislike":5,"score":31,"quote":{"pid":"e40437d31918a355293672f5ceeca959e99